  "title": "E-Commerce Picker and Packer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Pick and pack online orders</strong> with speed, care, and accuracy from our retail store.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and <strong>schedule timely deliveries</strong>, ensuring smooth logistics.</li>\n  <li>Manage <strong>refunds or discounts</strong> for out-of-stock items—because transparency matters.</li>\n  <li>Work cross-functionally with the <strong>Retail and E-Commerce teams</strong> to ensure seamless order fulfillment and customer satisfaction.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>💪 <strong>What You’ll Bring</strong></h2>\n<p>Excellent communication, time management, and organization skills<br>\nA strong sense of <strong>responsibility and reliability</strong><br>\nCool under pressure, especially in a <strong>fast-paced, high-volume</strong> environment<br>\nA great team player who works well with others</p>\n<p>Be part of a brand known for <strong>quality, care, and freshness</strong><br>\nLearn the ins and outs of <strong>E-Commerce operations</strong> from one of Singapore’s biggest ecommerce brand<br>\nEnjoy <strong>training and growth opportunities</strong> as the business expands<br>\nBe part of a supportive team that thrives on <strong>efficiency and customer happiness</strong><br>\nStaff discounts on the freshest products in town</p>\n<h2>Ready to Be the Backbone of Our Online Shopping Experience?</h2>\n<p>If you're the kind of person who finds joy in organizing chaos, delivering happiness, and working with purpose—this is your moment.</p>\n<p>👉 <strong>Apply now and help us deliver products to the world, one order at a time.</strong></p>",
